Arnold Korff https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arnold_Korff 0 Arnold Korff (2 August 1870, Vienna – 2 June 1944, New York City) was an Austrian-born Hollywood actor and director. He appeared in a number of German and Austrian films before moving to the United States and resuming his career in America. He made his first appearance on the American stage in Denver in 1892.
